txt.en: Thank you for contributing your collection! Please place your items in the box to receive your reward.
Wanted: Blackened furs from beasts near Amon Raith. Deliver the items to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith.
'I will make certain that Agnes puts these to good use. Thank you.'
'Agnes asked for the furs. She would prefer that they come from bears, but any blackened fur can be used to create rough bedding.'
DNT HIDING CONTENT - Task: Blackened Fur
Nathan Hodges, at Amon Raith, awaits the collection and delivery of blackened furs.
Deliver the blackened fur to Nathan Hodges at Amon Raith
Wanted: Blackened furs from beasts near Amon Raith.
